title: My Pixel 3a came with other apps installed with at total of 16gb.
content: My Pixel 3a came with 16gb of "other apps" already on my phone before I even installed any of my apps. Was wondering how this is because if you add up those apps they don't even come close to that. Was wondering if there is a fix for this so I don't start running out of storage. Thanks.
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 3a
